Hey guys,
I want to introduce you both / connect you all on this email. David is a great friend and a long time loyal S4 customer.
He is now using Harbortouch POS for is restaurants and bars. He is processing a significant volume of business and
pays a sizeable amount in processing fees. David's brother Mark is also in the restaurant space, and a partner in
several establishments in center city Philadelphia.
David and Mark are very interested to see if First Data (Card Connect) would present a better value proposition
than their current processor. David and Mark also represent a pretty big referral opportunity to other quality
establishments. This should be a great opportunity for you guys.
It is worth noting that the only reason David has not moved to S4 for payments (instead of the built in HT
payments) is because of your restrictions with HT. This includes:
1. SkyTab not working / being supported with HT
2. Lighthouse reporting restrictions
3. No support for rewards to the S4 customer program because of an existing deal with HT
4. Some other items, but generally a very restrictive relationship
For David, not having SkyTab and Lighthouse is a big issue.
I'd like you all to connect, see if First Data makes sense for David. Please keep me in the loop on this.
Best,
